    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="0">
        <title>HEATER COILS</title>
        <para>The heater coils are most efficient when the coils, fins and air flow passages are kept clean and free
            from dirt and dust. The coils should be cleaned with a soft flow of compressed dry air or vacuum and a soft
            brush. Damaged fins should be straightened to prevent air flow restrictions.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
